    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and would make a solid daily driver or a great project for someone willing to put in a little work. The exterior shows its age with several noticeable scratches, minor door dings, and some fading on the clear coat on the roof and hood. Inside, the upholstery has some visible wear and a small tear on the driver's seat, though all electronics and gauges remain functional. Mechanically, the car starts and runs, but it will eventually need attention for a slow oil leak and a suspension that is beginning to feel a bit soft. It\u2019s a reliable runner as-is, but it\u2019s priced to reflect the cosmetic and mechanical TLC it needs.",
