    {
      "id": "sybil_9_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty ride, and honestly, it\u2019s been such a joy to drive. It\u2019s in really solid shape and has plenty of life left in it for its next adventure! Whether you're commuting or hitting the road for a weekend trip, this car is ready to go. Come take it for a spin\u2014you're going to love how it handles!",
