      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Up for sale is a meticulously maintained 2018 Audi Q7 3.0T Quattro, finished in a timeless Graphite Gray Metallic. This vehicle has been garage-kept and primarily used for highway commuting, which shows in its remarkably clean exterior\u2014save for a few minor stone chips on the front bumper. The interior is a sanctuary of comfort, featuring Nougat Brown leather seats that remain firm and supple, along with the high-resolution Virtual Cockpit and a premium Bose surround-sound system. Mechanically, the car is in excellent health; it has followed a strict factory maintenance schedule, with all records available for review. The tires have plenty of tread remaining, and the brakes were recently serviced to ensure a crisp, responsive driving experience. It delivers a smooth, quiet ride with the confidence of all-wheel drive, making it a perfect choice for a family seeking both safety and sophistication.",
